  "text": ". for calculating the diagrams. In the first approach the exact calculation of all loop integrals is performed, followed by their expansion in the external momenta. In the second approach we used asymptotic expansion [CITATION_1] and expanded the diagrams in external momenta before performing the loop integrals, finding the same result as with the first approach. The final expressions collected in Table VI are compact and simple.",
